Package org.opengis.example.util

Implementation of some interfaces from the org.opengis.util package. The SimpleName and related classes are built on top of the JNDI javax.naming package.

Every classes in this package are hereby placed into the Public Domain. This means anyone is free to do whatever they wish with those files.

Since:
3.1
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SimpleName
    A GenericName backed by a JNDI Name instance.
    SimpleName.Local
    A LocalName specialization of SimpleName.
    SimpleName.Member
    A MemberName specialization of SimpleName.Local.
    SimpleName.Scoped
    A ScopedName specialization of SimpleName.
    SimpleName.Type
    A TypeName specialization of SimpleName.Local.
    SimpleNameFactory
    A NameFactory for creating SimpleName instances.
    SimpleNameSpace
    A NameSpace defining the scope of SimpleName instances.
